    ...    msg=TEST_SECRET_ID not set. Create secret first.

    ${response}=    Delete secret    ${TEST_SECRET_ID}    expected_status=204

    Log    Deleted secret ${TEST_SECRET_ID} via API    INFO

Secret creation should fail with conflict
